{"tid":1467113,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"因應局勢發展，連仔會唔會開D新分區？","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:53:25.000Z","uid":16367,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd472778432e1270bf4c1fdf977b3c1a802a1418","tid":1467113,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"依家真係太撚多分析Post，集中哂係吹水台。<br />\n<br />\n開返三個分區<br />\n<br />\n1. 中計區 <br />\n<br />\n2.散水區 <br />\n<br />\n3.勇武區<br />\n<br />\n其實大家打咁多析文都係想上黎搵下認同感<br />\n<br />\n分流返，方便大家揀適合自己既風格，減少嘈交。<br />\n<br />\n每個人都可以跟據自己立場揀野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔霸住個吹水台，分享D Fact Checked / 集會 / 間民記者會 / Brainstorms 等等既Post。"},{"pid":"c34102af8aaf3474eb1dc67ce9319128d3dc94d1","tid":1467113,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726a318d0af53a5ba6078295bf0d0183ac3873f5","tid":1467113,"uid":144572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063556ee80b03d0f4fd94d39144fe6e833f3018f","tid":1467113,"uid":292067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"我係何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965152df1707fbfccabe9480afc199905171190f","tid":1467113,"uid":283465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b6041f92a10a42ee5d3349f6268b71b910bd29e","tid":1467113,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"063556ee80b03d0f4fd94d39144fe6e833f3018f","tid":1467113,"uid":292067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"我係何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:12:24.000Z","msg":"咁不同意見實有既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地又唔係一言堂<br />\n<br />\n隔住個mon點分邊個係人邊個係鬼。<br />\n<br />\n只不過係想將D人既論點分流做好D<br />\n<br />\n吹水台我相信係最活躍既一個分區。留返黎比人做資訊傳播喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f02978a2322bae76ede288d6f1514254f9d3ebe","tid":1467113,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:13:33.000Z","msg":"輕推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb354fa7928cfb11e466c9672db97339d2f4841f","tid":1467113,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:21:37.000Z","msg":"倒不如畀我哋自己開台<br />\n再另外開個台將多啲人上嘅台推上置頂"},{"pid":"e669605944d9d901ce67ba1f3dddff88f3b237c3","tid":1467113,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb354fa7928cfb11e466c9672db97339d2f